(38, '2020-12-21 20:11:53', 'terms.php', NULL, 36, 'Your agreement with MySecureVault.ca', 'Votre entente avec MySecureVault.ca', 'MySecureVault.ca, also known as MonCoffreFort.ca, is a website run by Mr Jean-Fran&ccedil;ois Courteau. The website is run from a personal datacenter located in Canada. When we use the terms \"we\", \"us\", \"our\", \"MySecureVault.ca\" or \"MonCoffreFort.ca\", we refer collectively to the website and Mr Courteau. When we use the terms \"terms of use\" or \"Terms\", we refer to these terms of use.<br><br>Please note that these Terms of use constitute a binding legal agreement between you and us. By visiting our website, registering an account or using our services, you acknowledge that you have read the Terms, understand them, and agree to be bound by these Terms. If you are using the Services on behalf of an organization, you are agreeing to these Terms for that organization and acknowledging that you have the authority to act on behalf of that organization and commit to these Terms on behalf of that organization. If you do not agree with these Terms, please do not use our Services.', 'MonCoffreFort.ca, &eacute;galement connu comme MySecureVault.ca, est un site web op&eacute;r&eacute; par M. Jean-Fran&ccedil;ois Courteau. Ce site web est desservi depuis un centre de traitement personnel situ&eacute; au Canada. Lorsque nous utilisons les termes \"nous\", \"notre\", \"MySecureVault.ca\" ou \"MonCoffreFort.ca\", nous r&eacute;f&eacute;rons collectivement au site web et &agrave M. Courteau. Lorsque nous utilisons les termes \"conditions d\'utilisation\" ou \"Conditions\", nous r&eacute;f&eacute;rons aux pr&eacute;sentes conditions d\'utilisation.<br><br>Veuillez noter que des Conditions d\'utilisation constituent une entente l&eacute;gale entre vous et nous. En visitant notre site web, en cr&eacute;ant un compte ou en utilisant nos services, vous reconnaissez avoir lu les Conditions, que vous les comprenez, et vous acceptez d\'&ecirc;tre li